      <h2 class="section__heading">Multi-state Florida businesses.</h2>
      <p class="section__lede">Many Florida businesses operate across state lines &mdash; particularly into Georgia and Alabama, and for seasonal owners, the Northeast. Multi-state engagement scoping is part of every applicable Florida engagement.</p>
